ity [Grant A*MIDEX]. J. Resende was supported by Portuguese public funds [Project Reference NORTE-01-0145-FEDER-028540] and through FCT (Fundaç?o para a Ciência e a Tecnologia) [Project Reference POCI-01-0145-FEDER-006890].Supplemental Material: The online appendix is available at https://doi.org/10.1287/mnsc.2022.4298.
